These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, soy-milk
House: palace, futuristic, craftsman
3 different pets are kept: turtle, fish, cat
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, designer, mechanic
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, d&b, dubstep
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, comedy, horror
3 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly, chess
 1. the person playing backgammon is the person watching comedy movies##1
 2. the person playing chess is the mechanic##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person watching horror movies and the person drinking mirinda##2
 4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 5. the designer is the craftsman house##1
 6. the owner of the cat is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the palace house##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the fan of country##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the designer##1
10. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | soy-milk   | 7up           |
| House          | futuristic       | craftsman    | palace         |
| Pet         | fish    | cat  | turtle        |
| Job           | accountant | designer   | mechanic      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b        | dubstep    | country       |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy     | fantasy  | horror       |
| Game         | backgammon     | monopoly | chess |

