The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, bellflower, azalea
3 different pets are kept: dog, horse, pony
City: hamburg, paris, hannover
 1. the owner of the pony is the person who growsbellflower##1
 2. the owner of the pony is the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 4. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 5. the person who growsazalea is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking juice is the person who likes light-blue##1
 7. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
 8. the cape-cod house is the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
10. the owner of the pony is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | sprite    | juice         |
| House          | cape-cod    | craftsman | gothic-revival          |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | disaster  | animation     |
