3 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta, backgammon
3 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, mouse
City: prague, miami, venice
 1. the person eating kale is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the person playing backgammon is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person who growspoppy is the person eating peas##1
 4. the person who growslily is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 6. the person who growslily is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person playing canasta and the dressmaker##2
 8. the person playing canasta is on the left of the librarian##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person eating kale##1
11. the person playing canasta is the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
