The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, weightlifting, surfing
House: tower, gothic-revival, ranch-style
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, car, roller
 1. the person driving the car is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is the ranch-style house##1
 3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
 4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 5. the person who's sport is golf is between the person watching disaster movies and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 6. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 7. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the aristoff-smoker is the person driving the roller##1
 9. the person drinking milk is between the aristoff-smoker and the prince-smoker##2
10. the ranch-style house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
