 3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person playing chess##1
 5. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 7. the person who likes white is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's birthday is in june##2
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 9. the person playing chess is the person who likes ebony##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
11. the person who likes ebony is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta      | tea      |
| Hobby         | drawing     | hiking     | singing  |
| Game   | snooker | mah-jongg  | chess |
| Birthday   | april  | may     | june |
| Pet           | bird        | guinea-pig | fish     |
| City         | san-francisco    | venice | boston   |
| Color     | lilac        | white        | ebony   |

